<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style type="text/css" media="screen">
    body{
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
    }
    .keys__overlay{
      margin: 0 auto 0;
      min-height: 72vh;
      position: relative;
      width: 70%;

    }

    @media(max-width: 500px){
      .keys__overlay{
        width: 80%;
      }
    }

    .keys_content{
      margin: 0 auto 0;
      position: relative;
      width: 50%;
    }

    .keys__title{
      font-size: 34px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .keys__text{
      color: #4a4848;
      line-height: 23px;
    }

    .keys__image{
      width: 100%;
    }

    .h3_how{
      font-size: 25px;
    }

    .blue-link{
      color: #00bbff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="keys__overlay">
    <div class="keys__container">
      <div class="keys__title">Thank you for Upgrading!</div>
       <div class="keys__content">
         <p class="keys__text">
            The next step is to log in to your account  at <a class="blue-link" href="<%= I18n.t('website_config.website_address') %>/users/sign_in" target = "blank">color-preview.jp</a> and complete the step below. Then visit the <strong>'Library'</strong> section where you can drag & drop your new colors to load them into the color wheel.
         </p>


         <h3 class="h3_how">How to activate:</h3>
        <div class="keys__description">
          <%= image_tag 'directions_all_2X.gif', class: 'color_picker_arrow right keys__image' %>
           <!--  <%# if true %>
              keys
            <%# else %>
              key
            <%# end %>
          below: -->
        </div>

        <!-- <ul class="key__list">
          <%# @licenses.each_with_index do |license, i| %>
            <li class="key__item">
              <span class="key__index-number"><%#= ( i + 1).to_s %>:</span>
              <span class="key__value"><%#= license.key %></span>
            </li>
          <%# end %>
        </ul> -->

     
        <p>
          If you have any questions, email us here:
          <%= link_to I18n.t('website_config.contact_email2'), "mailto:#{I18n.t('website_config.contact_email2')}",
              class: 'blue-link' %>
        </p>
       
        <!-- <span class="keys__team">The <%#= I18n.t('website_config.app_name') %> Team</span> -->
      </div> 
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>